{"tid":1096020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為申請延期開庭 因美政府通知已透過對付敵國間諜和恐怖份子手段獲得證據","createTime":"2019-04-07T12:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T14:45:52.000Z","uid":119393,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b13a0b88cfdacd6d14a2fed54d0ea7dba6662e9d","tid":1096020,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:15:22.000Z","msg":"咁多日冇人講, CCTVB又好似冇報<br />\n<br />\n  美訴華為案4日上午在布碌侖下城區的聯邦紐約東區法院再次開庭。代表政府的檢方爆出驚人消息，美國當局為了掌握華為資料，動用了秘密監控設備，這類設備一般被用於跟蹤調查間諜活動嫌疑者。<br />\n<br />\n  助理檢察官Alex Solomon在4日開庭時指出，政府通過&ldquo;涉外情報監控法&rdquo;(FISA)獲得的證據需要保密處理。政府通知華為方面，他們打算將這些秘密獲取的信息用於檢控，而這部分證據是通過電子監控設備和人身搜查獲得。<br />\n<br />\n  據了解，涉外情報監控法批准下的秘密監控，需通過特別法庭開出搜查令，通常這類調查用於涉嫌外國間諜活動的對像。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  三位華為代表律師則表示，需要更多時間研究訴訟材料，希望延期開庭，獲得女法官Ann Donnelly准許。<br />\n<br />\n  下次開庭時間為6月19日。<br />\n<br />\n  此前根據路透社報道，美國當局收集華為活動的證據，方法之一即包括在機場秘密復制電子公司高管的電子設備數據。<br />\n<br />\n  華為公司上月14日在紐約首次過堂，被起訴13項聯邦罪名，包括電信欺詐、銀行欺詐、違反伊朗制裁令、妨礙司法公正等。華<br />\n<br />\n  為首席財務官孟晚舟也在該案被告之列。代表律師James Cole當庭宣布對所有指控不認罪。<br />\n<br />\n  孟晚舟去年12月在加拿大溫哥華被捕，目前取保候審中。美國司法部在1月底正式宣布起訴華為公司與孟晚舟，並尋求加拿大將其引渡至美國接受檢控。 <br />\n<br />\n英文版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-huawei-tech/by-spying-on-huawei-us-found-evidence-against-the-chinese-firm-idUSKCN1RG29T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-huawei-tech%2Fby-spying-on-huawei-us-found-evidence-against-the-chinese-firm-idUSKCN1RG29T&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e0a45094\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-huawei-tech%2Fby-spying-on-huawei-us-found-evidence-against-the-chinese-firm-idUSKCN1RG29T&h=5fd1f2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-huawei-tech/by-spying-on-huawei-us-found-evidence-against-the-chinese-firm-idUSKCN1RG29T</a>"},{"pid":"25a9b5101c170c87ad1e22db623dfb0f3984862b","tid":1096020,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16a32bdc9e67c03e2233250519b44aea4654e48","tid":1096020,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79731e214f0ee98cc94b85e61595ea891ca637af","tid":1096020,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faa360227d6d42cda08e1fba978aadfa96ec359","tid":1096020,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國當局為了掌握華為資料，動用了秘密監控設備，這類設備一般被用於跟蹤調查間諜活動嫌疑者。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華為 =  間諜活動"}]}